text: Terangganu (; Jawi:ترڠݢانو, Terengganu Malay: Tranung) formerly spelled Trengganu or Tringganu, is a state in Malaysia on the northeastern part of Peninsular Malaysia. The capital city of Terengganu is Kuala Terengganu. ==References== ==Other websites== *Terengganu State Government Information Portal *Tourism Malaysia - Terengganu *Terengganu tourism page
